 can&#39;t figure out, so a good layout and intuitive tools are a must. For example, most people look for the save button in the upper left-hand area of software, so good software will have the save button located in that area.","Good software will also house other options in the menu where they make sense to an average user. Microsoft Word has set the standard in this software category because its layout is very easy to use and even new users can find what they are looking for with a clearly labeled, tab-style menu system. Google Docs also has this easy-to-use tab navigation.","Software can have good usability without tab navigation though. For example, the Word Perfect line has simple dropdown menus that are also easy to navigate. It all comes down to how well the software is designed with the user in mind.","If your computer has limited storage or you would like to be able to access your documents from other devices, you may want to consider choosing word processing software that offers cloud storage. Some brands offer a limited amount of cloud storage for free, while others offer it on a subscription basis."]},"id":"c4437364-c8c7-49d2-b56e-039797034e6b","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/WWKcR9tAW6Upc9t43bd4SY.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":false,"importSrc":"https://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/prod/large/49250-micrsoft-word-2007-box.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WWKcR9tAW6Upc9t43bd4SY.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"WWKcR9tAW6Upc9t43bd4SY","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WWKcR9tAW6Upc9t43bd4SY.jpg","alt":""},"id":"de9929fd-ae09-44f3-9cad-4727728d8d09","type":"image"},{"data":{"hawk":"{\"data-model-name\":\"Microsoft Word\", \"data-widget-type\":\"price\"}","linkText":"Visit Site","url":"http://click.linksynergy.com/link?id=Cty0dj6o3sg&offerid=402138.323026000&type=2&murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoftstore.com%2Fstore%2Fmsusa%2Fen_US%2Fpdp%2FproductID.323026000","specs":null,"subtitle":"","urlStyle