, some programs have drawing tools that let you add your own drawings and digital paintings to the document. The drawing tool can also be useful for adding signatures to documents without printing them out.","<strong>File Formats</strong><br/>When you&#39;re done with a text document, odds are you’ll want or need to share it with someone else. So, saving your document in a format that a friend or colleague can open on their computer is crucial. Because of this, your program should be able to save a document in different file many different formats, including rich text format, .doc, .txt, PDF and more.","<strong>Help</strong><br/>You’re not going to know how to use every feature right away when it comes to your new word processing software, even after a bit of use. This is why an easy-to-use help option in the software is so important. You should be able to click on the help button and look up any topic by using keywords.","Several software programs also allow you to hover your mouse pointer over an option or menu item and information on that item will pop up in a word bubble. Many word processing software brands also offer online help, tutorial videos and help articles.","<strong>Tools for Collaborating &amp; Sharing</strong><br/>If you regularly share documents or work on them with several different people, then you should look for collaboration features. A good tracking feature is important so that the document can be passed from one person to another on a project and each person will be able to see what the others added to the document. A reviewing pane is also helpful for viewing various changes made to a document in a list format next to your document.","Text highlighting and the ability to add comments are also important features for anyone who wants to keep track of or display important areas of the text in a document to others. Adding comments is also a good way to ask questions and get clarification from others working on the document.","A finished document sitting on a hard drive is of no use. Print and publishing options help you get that text out to the world by turning it into blogs, HTML, wikis and more with a few mouse clicks.","By considering these categories, you will be able to find the best word processing software that has the features you need for your projects. While you are considering your current needs, be sure to look for word processing software that not only provides basic features, but also allows you to grow as your needs and skills change."]},"id":"e74aed2a-62e0-4d6c-83bd-779cbfcdd0ba","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Related Product Reviews"},"id":"d5ad2bac-b40e-44e1-870e-847bacbd0a8c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://click.linksynergy.com/link?id=Cty0dj6o3sg&offerid=402138.323026000&type=2&murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoftstore.com%2Fstore%2Fmsusa%2Fen_US%2Fpdp%2FproductID.323026000\">Microsoft Word</a>","<a href=\"http://www.dpbolvw.net/click-3909869-10726570-1463178368000\">WordPerfect</a>","<a href=\"http://www.softmaker.com/en/softmaker-office-windows-textmaker\">TextMaker</a>","<a href=\"https://www.google.com/accounts/ServiceLogin?service=writely&passive=1209600&continue=http://docs.google.com/&followup=http://docs.google.com/&ltmpl=homepage\">Google Docs</a>","<a href=\"https://shopper.mycommerce.com/checkout/cart/add/28469-15?affiliate_id=22430\">Kingsoft Writer</a>","<a href=\"http://www.ability.com/default.php\">Ability Write</a>","<a href=\"http://www.ragtime.de/web/en/download/ragtime6.html\">RagTime</a>"],"type":"ul"},"id":"4618363e-0b61-4eac-9921-2d6e69ddd260","type":"list"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"comparison_page_465","url":"/best-word-processing-software","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-contributor","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-contributor","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Contributor","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"w5zRTt8zKNM8ERYhxFTX9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US